HB 682 Original 2026 Regular Session Dickerson
Abstract: Authorizes the use of veterans as school resource officers.
Present law authorizes local public school systems and nonpublic schools to enter into
agreements with local law enforcement agencies to provide for school resource officers.
Present law defines "school resource officer" as a peace officer.
Proposed law retains present law and expands the definition of "school resource officer" to
include veterans.
