Proposed law defines "veteran" as a former or current member of the U.S. Armed Forces or
organized militia of the several states and territories, including but not limited to a member
of the Army, Navy, Air Force, Space Force, Marine Corps, Coast Guard, Natl. Guard, Air
Natl. Guard, Reserves, State Guard, or a commissioned officer of the Public Health Service,
Environmental Science Services Admin., or Natl. Oceanic and Atmospheric Admin., or its
predecessor, the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey.
(Amends R.S. 17:416.19(B)(1))
